Package sailpoint.object

Interface Filter.FilterVisitor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Filter.BaseFilterVisitor, FilterRenderer, sailpoint.search.JavaMatcher, Matchmaker.CubeMatcher
    Enclosing class:
    Filter
    public static interface Filter.FilterVisitor
    Visitor interface that is accepted by filters to perform various operations. It is the responsibility of the visitor implementation to iterate through children on composite operations.
